{"tid":1098876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不小心拔掉隨身碟免驚！微軟 Windows 不會再要求「安全移除硬體」","createTime":"2019-04-09T11:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T12:27:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84aae7a3c453e76f630f7f5fe4e38a8115753892","tid":1098876,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"不小心拔掉隨身碟，微軟 Windows 左下方總是會跳出警告，告訴用戶這樣會傷害電腦。未來不用再擔心了！在 Windows 10 最新版本，微軟將「快速移除」（Quick removal）改為預設。檔案傳輸完畢，直接拔除隨身碟就可以囉！<br />\n<br />\n微軟於 Windows 10 1809 版本更新，將「快速移除」設為預設選項，方便用戶立即拔除隨身碟。官方表示這項設定可能會降低傳輸性能，用戶可以根據自身狀況，於開始按下右鍵，找到「硬碟管理」，於視窗下方對應的硬碟，按右鍵「內容」－「原則」自行更改設定。<br />\n<br />\n根據《The Verge》報導，「快速移除」選項早在去年十月就已經推出，微軟卻仍是以「更好的性能」為預設項目，主要是避免意外拔除造成檔案毀損，未來將能省去這一個步驟。"},{"pid":"157e7762799ada814bf4fbbcbce87981ad01fe4a","tid":1098876,"uid":81995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"拖左咁多年先整出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8a3de18f1045b9f8124b7d46695b63eb25b6c8","tid":1098876,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"157e7762799ada814bf4fbbcbce87981ad01fe4a","tid":1098876,"uid":81995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"拖左咁多年先整出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"之後再讀取要入電腦double click篤重新連接冇快接"},{"pid":"a182473fe512c53c1e6014a894cf398399d0968e","tid":1098876,"uid":55386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"安全移除下體"},{"pid":"cfadffd43c990581cd9861653c357f835277dff4","tid":1098876,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKsYi35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3